TextEng: What... dungeon?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Yeah, that's me: here for the dungeon.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그래, 바로 나야: 던전 때문에 왔어.

TextEng: No, I'm just passing through the area.
Text: 아니, 그냥 이 지역 지나가는 중이야.

TextEng: Yes, of course. It should make for an interesting challenge.
Text: 그래, 물론. 흥미로운 도전이 될 거야.

TextEng: I'll be going.
I can handle myself.
Oh, please. I've spit out the likes of you for breakfast.
Text: 아유, 웃기지 마. 너 같은 건 아침 식사로도 모자라.

TextEng: That sounds like a horrible contest!
All right, here. 100 gold.
Forget it.
Me gives 100 gold. Me not care.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> How about 75 gold?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me gots 75 golds enough?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I'll give you 50.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me gives 50 gold?
You *will* tell me. NOW!
Me gots big killing story! Make you next!
Text: 나 대단한 살육 이야기 있어! 너 다음 차례 만들어 줄게!

TextEng: Me not pay you moneys.
You need not worry of me. Me do this.
Text: 나 걱정 안 해도 돼. 나 할 수 있어.

TextEng: Me is tough. Me do this asleep.
Text: 나 강해. 나 자면서도 할 수 있어.

TextEng: Me not like idea of this at all! Yuckies!
Text: 나 이거 전혀 안 좋아! 더러워!

TextEng: What... dungeon?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me is here for bloody dungeon. Yes, me is... *whistle*
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 피투성이 던전 때문에 왔어. 그래, 나... *휘파람*

TextEng: Me just walk from here to there is all.
Text: 나 그냥 여기서 저기로 걸어가는 거야.

TextEng: Me think this could be fun for all.
Text: 나 이거 모두한테 재밌을 것 같아.

TextEng: Time to go bye.
